{"tid":681903,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"喺街場踢傷鍠迷","createTime":"2018-05-28T12:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T12:22:26.000Z","uid":100433,"like":22,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"85fa2ac35364e0c551f96d80932d0866c516daa8","tid":681903,"uid":100433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:08:11.000Z","msg":"琴日去街場踢波，見到對面隊一個著皇馬卡斯米路波衫嘅人。<br />\n喺一次防守入面，我唔小心兜腳踢左落佢上五寸下五寸到，佢訓低痛到死咁。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：佢    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：屌？街波咋喎，都咁撚矛？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：有幾矛呀？好正常咋喎，你隊愛隊啲球員都係咁踢咖㗎啦，你地平時都覺得冇問題㗎，踢到你，Sorry囉。<br />\n<br />\n然後佢冇聲出，個樣勁嬲。<br />\n<br />\n最後祝所有覺得特意踢傷對手喺冇問題嘅鍠狗比人用收山腳收山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3709d254a74e35ffe15078a14d10d0e89617bf43","tid":681903,"uid":136770,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"咁你咪好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a85c7e8a029e628faf7f015d57b0e7c1e2ef54","tid":681903,"uid":14866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9df7d838143b4ae98116db936e10afdb9220f7a","tid":681903,"uid":33730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:10:33.000Z","msg":"鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22bb30a41d2f731455791f1fc0c5037984d5d1c","tid":681903,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T12:10:46.000Z","msg":"收9佢山啦<br />\n之後同佢講，呢d係拉幕斯的熱血"},{"pid":"4ccc12d99247cdd3f3c47f18e22a1af553